{"tid":2031754,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁錦祥：提倡港獨是你們的權利，不能夠一切跟隨美國的態度！","createTime":"2020-05-23T15:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T04:02:31.000Z","uid":219007,"like":44,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6b78d2579da372a73b693af55ed0d74e185c99","tid":2031754,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DSKJlb2lAhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDSKJlb2lAhY&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=024f9dcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DSKJlb2lAhY</a><br />\n11:30<br />\n<br />\n現在好多年青人將整個希望放在美國上，策略可能係岩，但道德上是錯的，因為底線一定要由香港人自己劃。<br />\n<br />\n不能夠俞懷松一句叫你們不要提港獨就不提，因為你們有提倡港獨的自由權利，呢D係我地自己既事，不能夠因美國叫我地唔講就唔講。"},{"pid":"239ea1fe3dc3403781f3a07cb579a8bb491e85d7","tid":2031754,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71a8153026a750dc19b44e28ba2a6572c186cb7a","tid":2031754,"uid":101307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"正確態度"},{"pid":"9eae786aec6ee9543487d4d3ae2a7ab0a8bdd4a1","tid":2031754,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dd9bf758ae7f12137f40e1dadaba737279b3c3","tid":2031754,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"態度正確"},{"pid":"eedda9d365e326f2cb95b09d1232b183798b798e","tid":2031754,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:18:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=20754bd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"4e34523e15e87ac27373dd8e6e634184c62d4419","tid":2031754,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae6a47723d88cf3299ca24e395ba5116edbbf9b","tid":2031754,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"科學抗爭必勝法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031745</a>"},{"pid":"6d8e2a9798eba2d7ac1fe5397d350d4bf8bcfdc1","tid":2031754,"uid":84657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"其實冇本土意識 就算獨立到 咪又係俾其他文化侵入到<br />\n除咗叫美國幫手 自己都要建立返屬於香港人既野"},{"pid":"3073b36224053e332b3a93f9f8386f4b66e1b1ea","tid":2031754,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"e568f06ee0fd9c971606bb21ae278c30303d9f42","tid":2031754,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effc94fe116d57dee8b5f2bf26be8a6deb47e921","tid":2031754,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"民族自強<br />\n香港獨立"},{"pid":"cfe0ca904e17b6425152801a363cab289d43c191","tid":2031754,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"態度正確"},{"pid":"f28af276ea5a7db374bd2ab8ba24b435dc39d215","tid":2031754,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa18d07cd32757d7e9e50a25bb4ba3469e910fb6","tid":2031754,"uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    台灣正名獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    滿洲獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    南蒙古自行獨立或與北蒙古組成聯邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    圖博獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    東突厥獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}